      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and has been genuinely cared for over the years! You'll find it drives smoothly and reliably, with only the minor, normal signs of everyday use you'd expect \u2014 think small interior scuffs and light exterior wear, nothing that affects performance or enjoyment. It's been kept up mechanically and is ready to hit the road without any major concerns. A solid, dependable choice for buyers who want quality without paying mint-condition prices!",
