    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a practical, budget-conscious option for buyers who need reliable transportation without paying a premium for cosmetics. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including multiple scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents consistent with years of everyday use. The interior is functional but shows its age \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or minor repairs may be needed in the near term. This is an honest, no-frills used car priced to reflect its actual condition \u2014 ideal for a commuter or someone looking for an affordable second vehicle.",
      "price": 18500.0,
