    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition at $45,000, and that price reflects exactly what you're getting \u2014 an exceptional example that stands out in any crowd. The exterior is flawless: the paint is deep, rich, and mirror-like with absolutely no scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel is straight and true, the trim is pristine, and the glass is crystal clear. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 the seats show no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface is clean and intact. All electronics, controls, and features function perfectly without exception. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. The mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and drivetrain \u2014 are all in top working order. Service history is consistent and up to date. This is a vehicle you can buy with complete confidence, drive immediately, and be proud to own.",
      "price": 45000.0,
